column5: I looked out the back door a few minutes ago and found these 15 fatties hanging out in the yard.  Guess they know Thanksgiving is over
Quick Lew,Christmas is soon. Rustle one down.
I'm sure there is a number of us who would be willing to help you out with those nuisance turkeys.
I'm sure there is a number of us who would be willing to help you out with those nuisance turkeys.   Never mind Rob. If he,s anything like me mudder,he,s given them names.

enuff silliness. that's sweet lew. you seem to have your own private zoo. keep them coming
